Global setup:

 Download and install Git
  git config --global user.name "Alistair Atkinson"
  git config --global user.email alatkins@gmail.com
  Add your public key
        

Next steps:

  mkdir Tupleware
  cd Tupleware
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:akatkinson/Tupleware.git
  git push origin master
      

Existing Git Repo?

  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:akatkinson/Tupleware.git
  git push origin master
